{
  "stem": "10572.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wrote to Captain Dane of British military intelligence and told him that not only did I have proof positive, but I was in counterintelligence, and I was-- that was my specialty, and that there was no doubt in my mind that many, many times I had gotten a phone call from them when he answered Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had the [NON-ENGLISH] to find out later on that Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Mercantaler was put in jail again after my affidavit arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he died in jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was still at Buchenwald, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he got-- ultimately he got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know where he had gone, where they had taken him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there were so many concerns that you didn't know how to sort them out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you just had to take every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told in the story that the only thing that I think made my father and me survive was the thought of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hamilton, that there was this woman in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would hear about this, would read about it, and would do something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the 14th of November, while we were still in Buchenwald, the affidavits arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So-- and this was before she got my letter that I'd written her on the 9th of November.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- as I have often said during those 50 years, if it wasn't for this unbelievable woman, I would have gone up the chimney like six million others.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very difficult.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't sleep in my bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I had gotten used to the hard, wooden boards, and my mattress was too soft.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I couldn't quite understand how people could live the soft life after seeing-- after having seen-- and-- and also living with this guilt of knowing that there were thousands of my buddies still there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was back home and being pampered by my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I-- I said to my father on day, I said, you know, I somehow feel that I, going out, the way I look, I'm the walking conscience of those bastards.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I made it very, very clear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went one day-- I went to this one that I told you about, this professional photographer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I needed an ID card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went in to her atelier, in her photo atelier, and when she saw me, she almost passed out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that somewhere, somehow gave me a satisfaction, you know, Because I wanted them to know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't tell them the details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But all they had to do is look at me and look at my eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I would-- that I-- that I was treated well, that there was no physical damage, you know, which was another thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were checked out before we were finally released by a prison doctor, by a prisoner who was a physician.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had to check, go over, see if everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was scared at that time because of the damage they had done to my back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't use sophisticated equipment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't know, and I didn't tell them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I thought that I might have blue spots and so on, but I passed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But these were these constant fears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You never know what is the next thing that will screw it up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- our workshop was still there, and I worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I made a suit for my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I continued to work, not professionally, but--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was holding up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was the brave, unbelievable woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She caved in afterwards, after we didn't need her strength anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the affidavits were there, but the-- our waiting number-- you know, there were waiting numbers that they told us that we might not be eligible to get our visa the next fall, fall '39.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had a friend at the tax office who was a German, a Gentile German, and who had been a war hero during the First World War but was known of being very, very philosemitic and one day called my father in and said to him-- his name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He called my father in and he said, get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Get out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever you have to do, get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, get your son out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father said, well you know, we don't have any chance until-- he said, get across the green border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just get out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, there will be war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "War will be soon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had some information that we didn't have yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
